<span foreground='Black' weight='bold' size='xx-large'>Creating a contact</span>

To create a <b>Contact</b>, you can click the <b>"+" button</b> above the <b>Search Bar</b>.

You can also click on the <b>File</b> menu,
and then on the <b>New Contact</b> button.

After either of these actions, the <b>New Contact View</b> will pop up in the <b>Main View</b>:
and you can enter your <b>Contact</b> into the <b>Entry Bars</b>.

After you are done entering your <b>Contact</b>, you can press the <b>Save Button</b>,
and the <b>Contact</b> will be saved.
